Sealer Machines

Dmach automatic tube sealer is a solution for creating perfect tube segments and offering a maximum of flexibility to the user. Automatic tube sealer has an intelligent cooling system system. Individual units can be used in standalone mode or combined freely to make a segmenting device with high variety of segment sizes.
